    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all thirteen factors and concluded that, taken in aggregate, the simulation evidence provides sufficient confidence to support the intended use. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification demonstrated that hemolysis predictions remain below the clinical threshold across the operating envelope. The team judged that remaining gaps are bounded and do not materially affect the decision.",
